headline: Is It Too Late to Consider Fox After a 38.4% Year To Date Surge?
summary: Wondering if Fox is still attractive after its big run, or if you are late to the party? This breakdown will help you decide whether the current price makes sense for long term investors. The stock has climbed to around $67.79, with gains of 3.5% over the last week, 4.6% over the last month, and 38.4% year to date, as well as 45.6% over the past year. This builds on multi year gains of 125.3% over three years and 146.7% over five years. That momentum has been shaped by a steady stream of...
